metadata.name: Come Together
metadata.description:
Collaboration with Jason Chambers x ThalamusT. 

Cubism meets The Whimsicals! In this case, the naughtier counterparts - The Wilfuls. They are subdued in the presence of Cubism royalty. 

Thank you, Jason, for giving me this opportunity to collaborate with you. It is my absolute honour! Hope to have more and more of such in future!
